Installation
============

To install the ODS:Gulf96 campaign, just copy all the files in the 
distribution archive to the main Tornado directory on your hard disk,
most likely c:\tornado.

Then, start GULF96.EXE. This will unpack the campaign files into the 
amp\map5 subdirectory. 

Read gulf96.txt for a briefing about this new campaign.

If you want more Iraqi resistance, try the ODS Enhancement Patch by
TCSC Associates which is included in this package. Read the file 
ODS_enh.DOC for details.


Have fun!


